data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***!!!Price Drop!!!****     This lovely two bedroom, one bathroom home is the perfect blend of comfort, style, and security. The newer floors and security system provide peace of mind, while the open floor plan creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The living area is spacious enough to accommodate a large sectional, making it perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. In the kitchen, modern appliances and ample storage space make meal preparation a breeze. The bedrooms are cozy and inviting, with plenty of natural light and closet space. The tastefully designed bathroom features modern fixtures and finishes.    The large yard and deck offer plenty of outdoor space for entertaining, barbecuing, or simply relaxing in the sun. The washer and dryer add convenience and make laundry day a breeze. Hurricane shutters provide added protection from inclement weather, while the carport and shed provide ample outside storage. Located near shopping, dining, and recreation, this home offers a comfortable and secure living experience that is perfect for anyone looking for a peaceful retreat.
